        "Achieve high-performance computing capabilities with Azure Virtual Machines. Store massive data sets on Azure Storage (Blob Storage and Data Lake Storage).",
        "Automate redundant tasks, predict equipment maintenance needs, and optimize construction projects through smart algorithms.",
        "Take full control of Azure AI services for custom AI models and Azure Machine Learning for developing and deploying predictive models and analytics solutions."
